al\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2FHKOnlinePortal&d=zLwroC9fIdX4jZfhKexof73SwEGp2Am2GayPy7qPUJ4%3D&h=2aabf976\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/HKOnlinePortal</a><br />\n<br />\nLike retweet reply<br />\n*如果見到想用嘅圖已經有手足用咗請搵第二張圖<br />\n*如果見到已經有好多圖就唔好再放圖，只留文字（短短地都得）<br />\n*唔好只係扔低張圖咩字都唔打<br />\n*唔知留咩好就like 手足留言或者啲對我哋有利嘅留言<br />\n<br />\n將Twitter 變成日常，每人每日做少少。<br />\n每人嘅一小步加埋就係一大步。<br />\n我哋唔知做咩先有用，所以咩都試下咩都做下"},{"pid":"5cd7488bf26be704d7658f77ce3de73d3bc3268f","tid":2018603,"uid":37525,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T04:52:04.000Z","msg":"如果我地唔做黃絲做紅衛兵<br />\n父母會有咩下場<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可以同藍屍父母洗腦<br />\n好在我哋做黃絲 反共<br />\n唔係做紅衛兵 奶共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"febb7f0d70a264ddf07b8267208adf4f9c46ada9","tid":2018603,"uid":104804,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5cd7488bf26be704d7658f77ce3de73d3bc3268f","tid":2018603,"uid":37525,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T04:52:04.000Z","msg":"如果我地唔做黃絲做紅衛兵<br />\n父母會有咩下場<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可以同藍屍父母洗腦<br />\n好在我哋做黃絲 反共<br />\n唔係做紅衛兵 奶共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T05:12:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Uc8iFTC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUc8iFTC.jpg&h=679bed6c&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n依家改習主席<br />\n日日批鬥老豆老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3d4dbf7fbcb43a8a570cbcf22cf43e7e00ef179","tid":2018603,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":